- Do not build your own base components, but rely on shadcn
- Components are added using shadcn CLI:
  ```
  npx shadcn@latest add --yes --overwrite <component>
  ```
If you're unsure if a component exists in shadcn, you can run:

```
npx shadcn@latest add --help
```